<paragraph id="8F8368C9881BA8207C246AF152D27E35" pageId="6" pageNumber="149">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="435BFEB9EC2D91456B30AD23C001D42D" pageId="6" pageNumber="149">This new species almost the same as its congeners, but the frons without blackish longitudinal stripe; lobes of male 9th abdominal tergite with roundly truncate apex.</paragraph>
